*zeitgeist-0.9.15 (03 Mar 2015)

  03 Mar 2015; Gilles Dartiguelongue <eva@gentoo.org> +zeitgeist-0.9.15.ebuild,
  +files/zeitgeist-0.9.15-fix-array-length-string-join.patch,
  +files/zeitgeist-0.9.15-python-detection.patch:
  Version bump, fix bug #518174. Move vala_src_prepare call after potential
  eautoreconf, fix configure to properly detect/use python, make unittest run
  within a dbus session, do not install docs in multiple paths.

  04 Jul 2014; Patrick Lauer <patrick@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Remove unneeded useflag description from metadata.xml

